{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63d8dfa354","title":"给毛岸青的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9b5227cc60","index":0,"year":1960,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"63d8dfa354"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"46b8fd62a3","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛岸青，毛泽东的次子，当时在大连治病。"},{"id":"6c8f51d76c","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"思齐，即刘思齐，现名刘松林，1949年10月同毛泽东的长子毛岸英结婚。"},{"id":"f03d66eadf","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"少华，即张少华，现名邵华，1960年与毛岸青结婚。14]娇娇，即李敏，毛泽东的女儿。"}],"contents":[{"id":"78a929f435","type":"title","text":"给毛岸青\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354"},{"id":"46b8fd62a3","type":"paragraph","text":"岸青我儿：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354"},{"id":"6c8f51d76c","type":"paragraph","text":"前复一封信，谅收到了。甚念。听说你的病体好了很多，极为高兴。仍要听大夫同志和帮助你的其他同志们的意见，好生静养，以求全愈。千万不要性急。你的嫂嫂思齐回和她的妹妹少华以来看你，她们十分关心你的病情，你应好好接待她们。听说你同少华通了许多信，是不是？你们是否有做朋友的意思？少华是个好孩子，你可以好好同她谈一谈。有信，交思齐、少华带回。以后时时如此，不要别人转。此外娇娇也可以转。对于帮助你的大连市市委同志，医疗组织各位同志们，一定要表示谢意，他们对你是很关怀的，很尽力的。此信给他们看一看，我向他们表示表诚的谢意","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354"},{"id":"f03d66eadf","type":"subtitle","text":"祝愉快！父亲","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354"}],"page":{"id":"df6da3565e","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"63d8dfa354","start":139,"end":139}}}},"__N_SSG":true}